    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stone ribs running transversely, that is, spanning crosswise at right angles to the longitudinal (lengthwise) axis across the top of a vault.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
